==English==
{{wikipedia}}

A gravity bong is usually a homemade device used to smoke marijuana.  It consists of a 1 to 3 gallon plastic jug with the bottom cut completely out, and a hole cut into the plastic cap in which the bowl will be placed.  A tub or sink is filled with water and the jug is submerged in the water until only the top of the jug remains above water.  The bowl filled with marijuana is placed into the hole in the cap and is then lit.  The jug is then slowly lifted up.  The force of gravity keeps the water that is in the jug at the same level as the rest of the water in the tub so a suction is created filling the rising jug with smoke.  When the jug is almost out of the water and filled with smoke the plastic cap and bowl are removed, and the person's lips are placed over the opening in the jug.  The jug is then pushed hard down back into the water while simultaneously inhaling very deeply.  The result is a very large volume of smoke being 'injected' into the person's lungs at once.
